{"tid":997138,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"【不會開口說話】《Tom and Jerry》開拍真人版電影","createTime":"2019-01-27T01:52:37.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-27T09:19:38.000Z","uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"737ebdc2fa4afa3dbd4f78842b93f8524b37513d","tid":997138,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-27T01:52:37.000Z","msg":"近年不少人氣卡通都開拍真人版電影，最新有指卡通《Tom and Jerry》都會開拍真人版。<br />\n報道指真人版《Tom and Jerry》會由05年版本《神奇4俠》（Fantastic Four）導演Tim Story執導，預定今年7月在位於倫敦開鏡。《Tom and Jerry》是由William Hanna和Joseph Barbera於1939年5月8日創建的短片動畫，主要描繪了兩個主角Tom與Jerry之間的對抗，而真人版將會尊重原著動畫設定，兩位主角均不會講說話，主要靠誇張肢體動作來表達情緒。<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20190126/large/1548481822_807b.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20190126%2Flarge%2F1548481822_807b.jpg&h=a6613028&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"efd4f45d9656ff336aee24efdbc4035690dcabec","tid":997138,"uid":99627,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-27T02:58:20.000Z","msg":"戇鳩？"},{"pid":"b8b86d4d289242208c77d31872648d4c8a3d7b0a","tid":997138,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"efd4f45d9656ff336aee24efdbc4035690dcabec","tid":997138,"uid":99627,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-27T02:58:20.000Z","msg":"戇鳩？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-27T09:09:34.000Z","msg":"好明顯係"},{"pid":"ab56f001bfd13e2e92c6277685d07db9493558ae","tid":997138,"uid":61660,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-27T09:19:38.000Z","msg":"不如真係揾隻真貓拍"}]}